WEBVTT

00:56.890 --> 01:00.351
EPISODE 13

02:32.485 --> 02:33.528
Gosh, you scared me.

02:35.613 --> 02:36.739
Why are you sleeping here?

02:38.575 --> 02:40.743
Wait, did I snore?

02:42.036 --> 02:43.163
You even snore?

02:48.960 --> 02:51.212
Do you know how many times
I nearly fell off the bed?

02:52.755 --> 02:55.842
I can't even share a bed with Jae-in
because we push each other.

02:57.093 --> 02:59.220
Don't even dream of
sleeping over here again.

02:59.304 --> 03:02.473
- I'm going to sleep here if I want to.
- No. No way. You absolutely can't.

03:06.686 --> 03:07.812
End of discussion.

03:11.274 --> 03:12.692
Then let's do this.

03:14.903 --> 03:16.571
- Here.
- What are you doing?

03:17.989 --> 03:20.533
- Hey, what is this? What are you doing?
- Stay put.

03:20.742 --> 03:21.784
Like this.

03:22.702 --> 03:25.455
We can hold each other tight and go
to sleep so that I can't even budge.

03:27.498 --> 03:29.500
Okay, let's go back to sleep.

03:32.712 --> 03:33.713
Gosh, seriously?

03:34.672 --> 03:35.673
- Oh, no.
- Hold onto me.

03:39.677 --> 03:40.637
That hurt.

03:41.387 --> 03:42.430
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

03:43.056 --> 03:44.140
Actually, no. I'm not okay.

03:53.942 --> 03:56.611
I told you to come early and help me
make dumplings, not just to eat.

03:57.612 --> 03:58.988
Maybe I should just live with Dad.

04:01.616 --> 04:02.784
Hey, where's Jeong-in?

04:03.743 --> 04:04.994
She didn't come home last night.

04:06.412 --> 04:07.705
- Hi, Seo-in.
- Hi.

04:07.789 --> 04:08.873
Where did she sleep?

04:11.125 --> 04:12.210
At Yeong-ju's place.

04:13.586 --> 04:15.088
Call Yeong-ju.

04:15.672 --> 04:16.673
Mom.

04:17.924 --> 04:19.133
It's just...

04:21.302 --> 04:23.554
My daughter didn't come home last night.
Can't I even ask?

04:35.692 --> 04:38.236
Hey, that should be good enough.

04:42.532 --> 04:44.993
Are you upset with me
because I slept at Ji-ho's place?

04:48.621 --> 04:50.373
You seem upset.

04:52.500 --> 04:54.043
Gi-seok is on his way here.

04:56.587 --> 04:58.589
I lied to him that I'm not feeling well,

04:58.673 --> 05:00.633
but he insisted,
saying it won't take long.

05:00.883 --> 05:02.510
Why is he so bullheaded?

05:04.512 --> 05:06.431
I'm sorry. I'll take care of it.

05:07.682 --> 05:10.727
Will you go wait for him outside,
advertising that you slept with Ji-ho?

05:11.436 --> 05:12.520
I can do that.

05:16.065 --> 05:18.943
A guy, who he used to look down on,
took away what had belonged to him.

05:19.027 --> 05:20.570
I'm sure he's livid.

05:21.029 --> 05:23.489
- Am I an object or what?
- Do you think this is about love?

05:24.490 --> 05:26.868
He wants you back
only because you were his.

05:30.246 --> 05:32.123
Do you know what really worries me?

05:32.206 --> 05:34.584
Whether Gi-seok's strategy is lame or not,

05:34.667 --> 05:36.669
what if it works in the end?

05:38.755 --> 05:39.839
I do believe in you.

05:40.923 --> 05:42.967
But most people
won't approve of your relationship.

05:44.594 --> 05:45.887
Is Ji-ho dangerous or something?

05:46.387 --> 05:48.389
He'd be the perfect target for gossip.

05:49.223 --> 05:51.684
And in others' eyes,
you're just someone who cheated

05:51.768 --> 05:52.852
on her decent boyfriend.

05:54.312 --> 05:55.980
Even if people talk shit about me,

05:57.023 --> 05:58.441
I won't regret meeting Ji-ho.

06:11.037 --> 06:11.996
Hey.

06:12.705 --> 06:14.123
Yeong-ju won't be meeting with you.

06:14.624 --> 06:16.626
And I'll tell my parents about Ji-ho.

06:19.796 --> 06:20.838
Come again?

06:22.006 --> 06:23.132
Isn't that what you want?

06:23.716 --> 06:27.261
You're trying to suffocate me
by meeting people around me one by one.

06:27.970 --> 06:29.931
Your strategy is working.
It's driving me nuts.

06:30.640 --> 06:33.017
I'd rather just tell everyone
and get it over with.

06:33.476 --> 06:34.894
This is driving me up the wall.

06:37.438 --> 06:40.900
My patience is wearing thin as well.

06:47.657 --> 06:49.534
If you stop here,

06:50.368 --> 06:51.786
I'll just put it behind us, okay?

06:52.453 --> 06:55.248
Don't act as if you suddenly realized
that you were so in love.

06:56.082 --> 06:58.584
You just can't accept the fact
that I'm dumping you.

06:58.668 --> 06:59.794
Be honest, please.

07:01.170 --> 07:03.548
Yes, you are right about that.

07:05.675 --> 07:08.761
There are so many reasons
I can't help but do this.

07:10.513 --> 07:13.432
Do whatever you want. I'll do the same.

07:33.327 --> 07:34.704
Did you get yelled at by Yeong-ju?

07:35.830 --> 07:37.540
She didn't have all the ingredients.

07:49.177 --> 07:50.219
I'm calling it quits.

07:51.179 --> 07:53.347
I wanted to be like you,
but I just can't do it.

07:53.556 --> 07:54.682
I can't take this anymore.

08:02.356 --> 08:03.441
What's the matter?

08:04.108 --> 08:05.234
I'm so pissed off.

08:06.277 --> 08:07.904
I held myself back because of you.

08:08.404 --> 08:10.740
Why must I be patient?
Did we commit a crime or what?

08:12.325 --> 08:14.702
I'll tell them everything.
He can't keep doing this.

08:17.079 --> 08:18.206
Who do you mean by "he"?

08:20.625 --> 08:21.751
Gi-seok?

08:26.297 --> 08:28.132
Would telling your parents
change anything?

08:29.008 --> 08:29.926
No.

08:31.135 --> 08:32.136
But still...

08:34.805 --> 08:37.892
It'll only make things
more difficult for you. He won't change.

08:52.073 --> 08:53.115
Hi, Mom.

08:55.201 --> 08:58.579
I just called to check in.
I hung up because I had to do something.

09:03.334 --> 09:04.794
I slept at Yeong-ju's place.

09:09.298 --> 09:10.591
No, I didn't drink.

09:12.218 --> 09:14.428
No, we just hung out.

09:17.723 --> 09:18.808
I'm serious.

09:19.433 --> 09:22.270
She'd never call me for no reason.

09:24.397 --> 09:25.982
Are you sure she's at Yeong-ju's place?

09:27.108 --> 09:28.442
You can go there and find out.

09:29.485 --> 09:30.611
Why are you all annoyed?

09:32.446 --> 09:33.656
I have my fair share of stress.

09:34.532 --> 09:35.700
Because you got nothing to do?

09:39.161 --> 09:42.415
Has Jeong-in really told you nothing
about that guy?

09:45.543 --> 09:46.627
I met him once.

09:47.128 --> 09:48.337
You met him?

09:49.839 --> 09:53.342
Is their relationship already serious
enough for her to introduce him to you?

09:53.426 --> 09:56.887
No, I ran into them by chance.
We just said hello, and that was it.

09:57.597 --> 10:00.683
I heard he's a pharmacist who's her age.
That's what you told me.

10:01.976 --> 10:04.812
Yes. That's all you know
about him as well, right?

10:05.938 --> 10:06.772
Right.

10:09.984 --> 10:11.736
He has some sort of flaw, right?

10:14.822 --> 10:16.532
Jeong-in will tell you about it.

10:16.616 --> 10:17.992
So, he does have a flaw.

10:19.535 --> 10:22.330
It's her relationship,
so you should hear it directly from her.

10:22.872 --> 10:23.998
Just give her some time.

10:26.375 --> 10:28.210
Should I prepare myself mentally?

10:28.961 --> 10:30.921
It's very hard to get this.

10:31.380 --> 10:33.591
- I've only heard about this.
- You work for the country.

10:33.674 --> 10:34.967
I'll work around your schedule.

10:35.551 --> 10:37.053
Yes, anytime is good for me.

10:37.762 --> 10:39.096
Let's do that. Okay.

10:42.016 --> 10:45.519
That was Assemblyman Jang.
He pesters me to meet up constantly.

10:46.812 --> 10:49.023
I heard his youngest daughter
is a professor now.

10:49.106 --> 10:50.358
I bet he wants to brag about it.

10:50.691 --> 10:52.068
He already told me about that.

10:52.777 --> 10:55.112
His daughter is around the same age
as my son.

10:55.863 --> 10:57.239
He wants to set her up with him?

10:57.323 --> 10:59.617
Need I say more?
Obviously, that's what he wants.

11:01.369 --> 11:03.579
That's great.
This is like a pre-celebration, then.

11:05.081 --> 11:06.791
Take us all out for a fancy dinner.

11:08.459 --> 11:11.545
Is that why
you didn't invite Mr. Lee today?

11:15.633 --> 11:18.052
You're right. Mr. Lee isn't here.
You guys didn't call him?

11:21.180 --> 11:23.641
I assumed you'd bring him along.

11:25.309 --> 11:28.104
Wouldn't it upset him
if I call and invite him now?

11:29.647 --> 11:33.567
You guys should've thought of this.
This puts me in an awkward position.

11:35.236 --> 11:37.530
Gosh, he'll get the wrong idea.

11:37.780 --> 11:39.115
What should I do now?

11:42.993 --> 11:45.246
I shouldn't have left it up to you all.
It's all my fault.

11:46.038 --> 11:47.915
I called him too late.

11:48.457 --> 11:51.043
My apologies.
I'll clear up the misunderstanding.

11:51.127 --> 11:55.172
Mr. Park, you're always so organized
and thorough. Why today of all days...

11:55.798 --> 11:57.967
Gosh, you totally let me down.

11:58.050 --> 11:59.093
Unbelievable.

12:24.493 --> 12:27.371
I only came back because at least
I shouldn't stress you out as your wife.

12:29.457 --> 12:30.916
What has Seo-in decided to do?

12:31.834 --> 12:34.712
What kind of question is that? She already
made up her mind to divorce him.

12:35.296 --> 12:36.130
You couldn't even

12:36.213 --> 12:38.674
talk her out of it
when you stayed with her for days?

12:38.757 --> 12:41.427
Think about why she made
such a decision despite being pregnant.

12:42.720 --> 12:46.140
As her parents,
we should respect her decision.

12:47.641 --> 12:48.851
About Jeong-in...

12:51.645 --> 12:52.563
What about her?

12:53.522 --> 12:55.691
Jeong-in said there's a guy she likes.

12:57.026 --> 12:58.360
Tell her I'd meet him.

12:59.278 --> 13:00.362
Why all of a sudden?

13:01.697 --> 13:03.699
What about Gi-seok,
who you're absolutely fond of?

13:04.783 --> 13:07.495
You said we, as parents,
should respect our children's opinion.

13:59.838 --> 14:05.761
YU JI-HO

14:22.111 --> 14:24.113
KWON GI-SEOK

14:56.020 --> 15:03.027
WOORI PHARMACY

16:20.729 --> 16:21.647
Gi-seok.

16:22.147 --> 16:23.565
What brings you by?

16:27.861 --> 16:28.946
Is Ji-ho not home?

16:29.029 --> 16:32.074
I have to talk to him about something,
but I can't get a hold of him.

16:34.201 --> 16:36.412
- You're here too.
- He's not here now.

16:38.622 --> 16:39.707
Where did he go?

16:40.207 --> 16:42.584
We don't know. Yeong-jae and I stopped by,

16:42.668 --> 16:45.671
but he wasn't home when we got here.
We're just eating some fried chicken now.

16:46.088 --> 16:48.090
- Come in and join us.
- No, it's all right.

16:50.718 --> 16:52.761
All right, then. I'll see you guys around.

16:56.306 --> 16:57.558
- Bye.
- Bye.

17:00.978 --> 17:02.312
Why did you invite him in?

17:03.731 --> 17:05.065
Because I was baffled.

17:05.733 --> 17:06.692
By what?

17:17.244 --> 17:19.163
What baffled you so much?

17:20.330 --> 17:21.457
Talk to Ji-ho about what?

17:22.249 --> 17:25.044
- He obviously came looking for Jeong-in.
- No way.

17:26.295 --> 17:27.463
Why else would he come here?

17:28.088 --> 17:31.717
He must be so embarrassed right now
because we saw him here.

17:32.217 --> 17:33.552
You think so?

17:35.512 --> 17:38.057
Why did Jeong-in accept the ring
to begin with?

17:38.974 --> 17:41.769
Gi-seok seems to think
that she accepted his marriage proposal.

17:42.561 --> 17:43.604
Give me a break.

17:43.687 --> 17:48.609
He proposed to her
fully knowing that she wouldn't accept it.

17:49.276 --> 17:52.863
This is more than just being clingy.
I'd say it's an obsession.

17:54.948 --> 17:56.408
If we look at it positively,

17:57.034 --> 17:59.745
it could also mean
that he loves Jeong-in that much.

18:00.996 --> 18:02.039
If that's love,

18:02.122 --> 18:04.541
having a crush on someone
would count as a dating experience.

18:06.001 --> 18:09.588
By that logic,
you've dated about 15 girls.

18:11.006 --> 18:11.965
That's right.

18:26.688 --> 18:27.981
I already had lunch.

18:29.566 --> 18:32.194
I can have lunch at home.
Are you having a busy day?

18:32.528 --> 18:34.113
Why would you ask when I'm already here?

18:34.530 --> 18:35.823
What's up? Do you need something?

18:36.448 --> 18:37.866
Well...

18:38.992 --> 18:41.036
It's about the guy you mentioned.

18:41.870 --> 18:43.122
Your dad wants to meet him.

18:46.375 --> 18:47.334
Why?

18:47.876 --> 18:49.169
I was surprised too.

18:49.878 --> 18:52.506
He said he wants to respect your opinion.

18:56.301 --> 18:57.261
Did he...

18:58.595 --> 19:00.222
hear something from Gi-seok?

19:00.806 --> 19:02.933
No, it didn't seem to be the case.

19:05.602 --> 19:06.645
Hear about what though?

19:18.448 --> 19:20.075
Seo-in and Jae-in

19:20.159 --> 19:22.828
hinted at me
that I should mentally prepare myself.

19:24.329 --> 19:25.747
Let's hear it now.

19:25.831 --> 19:29.042
What is it?
Why are you scaring me like this?

19:31.128 --> 19:33.755
Whatever it is, I'm prepared to handle it.
Just tell me.

19:45.309 --> 19:46.560
Actually...

19:50.772 --> 19:51.773
He...

19:59.281 --> 20:00.407
He has a kid.

20:03.452 --> 20:04.411
Who?

20:05.329 --> 20:06.371
The guy I'm seeing.

20:10.292 --> 20:11.293
Mom.

20:13.503 --> 20:14.713
I'm sorry.

20:20.052 --> 20:21.011
Mom.

20:23.222 --> 20:24.056
You see,

20:24.806 --> 20:25.724
Jeong-in.

20:26.558 --> 20:29.061
- This is--
- I tried not to fall for him.

20:32.022 --> 20:33.065
I, too,

20:34.441 --> 20:36.193
thought it was wrong,

20:40.656 --> 20:41.657
but...

20:43.158 --> 20:44.409
I like him so much.

20:46.453 --> 20:48.038
I like him a lot, Mom.

20:49.957 --> 20:50.958
I'm sorry.

20:52.292 --> 20:53.293
Well...

20:54.836 --> 20:56.797
This isn't about you apologizing.

20:57.923 --> 20:59.132
Gosh, this is...

21:00.759 --> 21:01.927
I don't even know what to say.

21:02.803 --> 21:05.347
I can't be without him, Mom.

21:06.848 --> 21:07.975
I can't live without him.

21:10.352 --> 21:11.603
My goodness.

21:13.939 --> 21:14.982
I'm sorry.

21:16.066 --> 21:17.234
I'm sorry, Mom.

21:18.610 --> 21:19.736
But...

21:20.779 --> 21:23.073
help me, please.

21:24.700 --> 21:25.701
Gosh, Jeong-in...

21:27.035 --> 21:28.829
What should we do?

21:30.998 --> 21:32.082
Mom...

21:34.334 --> 21:35.502
My gosh...

21:40.590 --> 21:41.466
Jeong-in.

21:43.051 --> 21:44.761
What should we do about this situation?

21:48.265 --> 21:49.308
I'm sorry.

22:01.987 --> 22:03.280
You should get back to work.

22:07.826 --> 22:08.952
I'll call you.

22:09.703 --> 22:10.787
Mom, wait.

22:17.544 --> 22:18.587
I have a favor to ask.

22:21.882 --> 22:24.301
Why do you keep crying?

22:28.096 --> 22:30.432
I'd like you to meet Ji-ho.

22:33.477 --> 22:34.686
He's a good person.

22:38.482 --> 22:39.566
I'm sure.

22:40.525 --> 22:43.153
You must've fallen for him
because he's a good person.

22:44.780 --> 22:45.822
But...

22:47.032 --> 22:48.575
why should I meet him?

22:56.291 --> 22:57.918
Are you thinking...

23:08.386 --> 23:09.429
Hye-jeong.

23:10.097 --> 23:11.515
Why are you calling me so fondly?

23:12.933 --> 23:14.226
I need to step out.

23:14.893 --> 23:16.812
Why? Did something happen to Eun-u?

23:18.647 --> 23:19.648
No.

23:25.487 --> 23:28.323
I don't want to be blamed
if your relationship doesn't work out.

23:29.574 --> 23:30.700
I'll be quick.

23:32.702 --> 23:33.703
Don't bother coming back.

23:34.412 --> 23:36.039
Just be the first one to arrive tomorrow.

23:45.090 --> 23:46.591
If you want coffee, you can have this.

23:48.718 --> 23:49.553
No problem.

23:50.929 --> 23:52.097
You don't want coffee?

23:52.347 --> 23:54.933
I'm all right.
I have to finish a report quickly.

23:55.767 --> 23:56.768
Hey, actually...

23:58.436 --> 24:00.689
Does Ji-ho know that I came by his place?

24:01.898 --> 24:04.151
Yes, I told him you wanted
to talk to him about something.

24:05.902 --> 24:07.362
I had to talk to him about something.

24:07.445 --> 24:08.989
Yes, that's what I told him.

24:09.990 --> 24:11.241
- Right, you said that.
- Yes.

24:15.120 --> 24:17.164
- Don't you have to finish a report?
- Oh, right.

24:27.883 --> 24:28.884
Shit.

24:32.596 --> 24:34.097
God damn it.

24:39.144 --> 24:40.228
What the hell.

24:54.159 --> 24:55.202
Damn it.

24:59.956 --> 25:01.166
Jeez...

25:05.629 --> 25:08.340
- Where are you coming from?
- I had to go to the admin office.

25:10.008 --> 25:11.301
By the way--

25:11.843 --> 25:13.678
I'm sorry about last weekend.

25:14.262 --> 25:16.264
My wife and I had to go somewhere,

25:16.556 --> 25:18.600
so I couldn't attend the get-together.

25:18.683 --> 25:21.561
Is that right?
I wondered why you didn't come.

25:21.645 --> 25:25.982
If it happens again, I'll make sure
I let you know beforehand.

25:27.359 --> 25:28.818
- All right.
- Have a nice day.

25:35.158 --> 25:37.118
PRINCIPAL LEE TAE-HAK

25:48.463 --> 25:49.547
Yes, sir.

25:49.673 --> 25:52.425
I'm just calling to see if you'd be up
for grabbing dinner

25:52.509 --> 25:54.219
since you couldn't join us on the weekend.

25:54.719 --> 25:57.055
I'm sorry. I have plans this evening.

25:57.847 --> 25:59.766
Really? Then shall we
grab dinner tomorrow?

25:59.849 --> 26:03.478
No, it's all right. It's my fault
that I couldn't attend the get-together.

26:03.853 --> 26:06.648
- It would only make me feel more guilty.
- Oh, please.

26:07.649 --> 26:10.652
Anyway, all right.
Let's find another time, then.

26:10.735 --> 26:12.028
Sure.

26:12.487 --> 26:14.155
- I won't keep you from your work.
- Okay.

26:17.242 --> 26:18.451
Do you think I'm a pushover?

26:31.256 --> 26:32.549
- Hello.
- Yes, hello.

26:33.258 --> 26:34.509
What brings you by?

26:35.510 --> 26:38.555
I'm here to see Jeong-in.
I can't get a hold of her.

26:39.431 --> 26:41.391
Oh, really? Hold on.

26:43.268 --> 26:44.311
What is she up to now?

26:46.813 --> 26:48.982
Hey, Ha-rin. Is Jeong-in in the office?

26:49.190 --> 26:52.485
No, she isn't. By the way,
did something happen to Jeong-in?

26:53.236 --> 26:54.195
Why do you ask?

26:54.946 --> 26:56.239
She was crying earlier.

26:57.157 --> 26:58.450
Where is she now?

26:59.826 --> 27:02.370
- In the viewing room.
- It's on B1.

27:02.787 --> 27:05.290
- I see. Thank you. See you around.
- See you.

27:12.380 --> 27:13.465
Who is he?

27:14.716 --> 27:15.800
Is he that guy?

27:16.551 --> 27:19.054
- Who else would it be?
- I see.

27:19.637 --> 27:21.389
Hey, what's going on with Jeong-in?

27:22.223 --> 27:23.266
Who knows?

27:24.559 --> 27:27.520
I'd walk around with a huge smile on
my face if I had a boyfriend like that.

27:44.245 --> 27:45.330
What are you doing here?

27:50.752 --> 27:54.422
I just broke into tears
while talking to my mom.

27:55.590 --> 27:57.300
You didn't have to ditch work
to come here.

27:59.094 --> 28:00.762
Hye-jeong will speak ill of me.

28:11.481 --> 28:14.192
She let me leave, saying I may blame her
if things go wrong between us.

28:23.618 --> 28:25.286
It's nice to cry sometimes.

28:26.538 --> 28:28.164
I get to see you at this hour.

28:29.749 --> 28:30.917
You have to be stronger.

28:34.671 --> 28:36.214
I'm not crying because I got scolded.

28:37.799 --> 28:38.800
I just...

28:40.343 --> 28:41.428
For some strange reason...

28:44.264 --> 28:45.390
Why can't I cry?

28:46.891 --> 28:49.144
Yes, you can. But the thing is,

28:51.938 --> 28:53.148
I don't want you to cry alone

28:54.441 --> 28:55.984
especially when I'm not around.

29:03.450 --> 29:04.868
But you're here now.

29:07.787 --> 29:08.997
Okay, cry. Cry all you want.

29:15.503 --> 29:16.546
My mom...

29:19.299 --> 29:20.633
left without giving me her answer.

29:34.397 --> 29:36.065
I always tell you

29:36.941 --> 29:38.026
that everything will be okay

29:39.194 --> 29:40.820
and that we can take it slow...

29:43.698 --> 29:46.117
because there's this faith,
which only you and I know of.

29:50.663 --> 29:52.665
The "Us" you always talk about?

29:54.667 --> 29:56.753
Yes, us.

30:05.094 --> 30:06.596
By the way, what is this place?

30:09.057 --> 30:10.391
Where people kiss secretly.

32:26.653 --> 32:27.779
What else?

32:28.529 --> 32:30.698
His parents run a dry cleaner's.
That's all I heard.

32:32.158 --> 32:33.201
What about you?

32:34.994 --> 32:37.080
There's no need to hide anything now.

32:38.039 --> 32:39.082
I'm not hiding anything.

32:39.582 --> 32:41.584
We just said hello. That's all.

32:43.127 --> 32:45.797
He seemed like a nice guy.
He was polite as well.

32:48.758 --> 32:49.926
I can't believe this.

32:51.010 --> 32:53.304
I've never even imagined
that I'd be in this situation.

32:54.639 --> 32:55.515
What about Seo-in?

32:57.850 --> 32:59.227
She has a point.

33:01.437 --> 33:02.897
So what are you going to do, Mom?

33:04.482 --> 33:06.150
I have no idea.

33:06.693 --> 33:09.278
I can't even help you
sort out your situation.

33:11.823 --> 33:14.200
With Jeong-in's situation,
I feel even more clueless.

33:15.868 --> 33:19.789
Mom, Jeong-in wants to show you
that you don't need to worry.

33:20.540 --> 33:22.917
She wants you to know
that she's dating a decent guy

33:23.668 --> 33:26.254
and that you don't need
to sigh nonstop like this.

33:27.046 --> 33:28.965
I've never seen her
with those eyes before.

33:30.758 --> 33:32.343
I think she's thinking of marrying him.

33:33.344 --> 33:34.429
Already?

33:37.724 --> 33:38.891
You should meet him.

33:41.060 --> 33:42.854
I'm sure you don't want any regrets.

33:43.563 --> 33:46.482
You said you'll regret for the rest of
your life that you didn't dissuade me

33:46.566 --> 33:48.234
from marrying him hard enough.

33:49.444 --> 33:51.112
So don't be like that to Jeong-in.

33:52.530 --> 33:54.323
Mom, are you going to be against it?

33:58.995 --> 34:01.080
I don't know who this is,
but he's in deep trouble.

34:02.623 --> 34:05.251
Even just a slap in the face
can get you in serious trouble.

34:05.918 --> 34:09.172
Even if it's sex between a married couple,
it can be prosecuted

34:09.672 --> 34:11.591
if coercion or threats were involved.

34:12.550 --> 34:15.428
Even at our law firm, we get
many inquiries regarding marital rape.

34:16.888 --> 34:18.639
Hey, but they're married.

34:20.016 --> 34:21.184
It doesn't work that way.

34:21.434 --> 34:24.854
Legally, it's considered
violation of self-determination.

34:26.898 --> 34:28.024
By the way, who's this guy?

34:29.942 --> 34:32.695
Oh, my friend asked me to look into it
for his acquaintance.

34:34.781 --> 34:37.700
By the sound of it,
I don't think he's a nice guy.

34:38.493 --> 34:39.786
Don't befriend him.

34:42.747 --> 34:45.249
Let's play one more round
and go for drinks.

34:45.333 --> 34:46.375
- Sure.
- All right.

34:51.714 --> 34:52.799
Hey, then...

34:53.591 --> 34:56.385
If it's considered assault,
will he lose his parental rights as well?

34:57.470 --> 34:58.930
- In the case of child abuse...
- Yes.

35:00.932 --> 35:03.017
By any chance,
is this what you're going through now?

35:04.018 --> 35:05.853
Gosh, what are you talking about?
Of course not.

35:06.312 --> 35:07.438
- Right?
- Yes.

35:08.231 --> 35:09.941
You kept asking about it,
so I was curious.

35:11.025 --> 35:14.195
Even if this is your case,
don't ask me to represent you.

35:14.987 --> 35:16.989
There's no way he'll win the case.
He'll lose.

35:59.073 --> 36:00.867
- I have to make a quick phone call.
- Okay.

37:28.829 --> 37:29.997
What should we order?

37:34.710 --> 37:35.586
What are you up for?

37:37.213 --> 37:38.673
You eat more, so the choice is yours.

37:42.426 --> 37:43.511
I'll order a lot then.

37:49.141 --> 37:50.309
Let's see...

38:33.311 --> 38:35.021
I'll park the car. You head up first.

39:41.962 --> 39:43.172
Isn't this enough confirmation?

39:45.257 --> 39:46.342
It's like I said.

39:47.718 --> 39:48.928
I'm not you.

39:50.721 --> 39:52.139
This much I can take.

39:54.892 --> 39:56.352
You can date Jeong-in again...

39:58.813 --> 40:00.064
after we break up.

40:02.066 --> 40:02.983
Hey.

40:03.067 --> 40:05.736
I'm telling you this because

40:06.404 --> 40:08.614
it's your least pathetic
and realistic option.

40:11.534 --> 40:13.035
She'll open the window soon.

40:15.913 --> 40:17.164
You think I'm scared?

40:17.748 --> 40:18.707
I am.

40:20.501 --> 40:22.378
I worry about her finding out the truth of

40:22.753 --> 40:24.380
the man she once dated.

40:25.089 --> 40:26.924
Stop acting so high and mighty

40:27.925 --> 40:29.885
and ask Jeong-in to come down.

40:31.929 --> 40:33.681
Try taking her if you can.

40:34.974 --> 40:35.850
Is that a challenge?

40:35.933 --> 40:38.310
Show some respect first and then talk.

40:49.530 --> 40:53.075
All right, fine.
Do whatever you want. I'll let you.

40:54.410 --> 40:57.788
You can meet my family,
my friends, and those around me.

40:58.914 --> 41:00.749
Call me anytime and anywhere.

41:01.250 --> 41:02.918
Ask me to meet up and visit me.

41:03.794 --> 41:05.087
I'll put up with anything.

41:05.671 --> 41:06.922
What are you doing?

41:07.006 --> 41:08.591
So bug me all you want.

41:10.634 --> 41:13.012
I'll think
that I'm paying for hurting you,

41:14.138 --> 41:15.556
so until you're done,

41:16.348 --> 41:18.017
I won't resent you in any way.

41:18.934 --> 41:21.145
Do whatever you want until you get bored.

41:23.272 --> 41:25.983
- Go inside, Jeong-in.
- But don't bother Ji-ho.

41:27.568 --> 41:30.529
If you do, I'll do anything to stop you.

41:32.031 --> 41:33.491
I don't care who I have to go after.

41:47.630 --> 41:51.008
It took you half a day to open this door.

41:51.091 --> 41:52.968
What the hell took you so long?

41:57.306 --> 41:59.600
- It's been a while.
- Oh, hi.

42:01.060 --> 42:02.978
We'll talk later.

42:03.812 --> 42:04.939
Seo-in, follow me.

42:09.318 --> 42:10.444
We'll talk in here.

42:36.470 --> 42:38.639
You seriously asked Jae-in to stay here?

42:42.601 --> 42:44.019
Don't act naive.

42:44.979 --> 42:46.897
I know you saw this coming.

42:49.692 --> 42:51.068
I said there won't be a divorce.

42:51.735 --> 42:53.404
Leave if that's all you have to say.

43:06.709 --> 43:08.210
Give up my paternal rights?

43:08.294 --> 43:10.754
You're telling me
to stop being a human being.

43:12.965 --> 43:15.551
You proved yourself as an animal
when you kicked me.

43:17.720 --> 43:20.264
It's in the past and I already apologized.

43:21.557 --> 43:22.808
And that makes it go away?

43:24.476 --> 43:25.728
Just have your lawyer ready.

43:27.187 --> 43:28.772
What will you tell our baby then?

43:29.773 --> 43:31.066
Will you tell I don't exist?

43:32.109 --> 43:33.777
Why when you're perfectly alive?

43:34.653 --> 43:36.238
I'll say you're in prison.

43:42.578 --> 43:44.288
Jae-in, it's nothing.

43:46.373 --> 43:48.667
What was that? Were you about to hit her?

43:51.253 --> 43:52.463
Has he been hitting you?

43:53.964 --> 43:55.132
- Jae-in--
- Seo-in!

43:55.883 --> 43:58.052
Come on. Let's talk outside.

43:59.303 --> 44:00.387
Who the hell are you?

44:01.597 --> 44:02.848
Who are you to hit my sister?

44:03.515 --> 44:05.059
- Jae-in--
- Who are you to hit her?

44:05.559 --> 44:06.810
Who the fuck are you?

44:09.063 --> 44:11.607
- Jae-in, that's enough--
- Let go.

44:11.690 --> 44:13.734
Hit me too. Go on.

44:13.817 --> 44:16.278
- Jae-in, come on.
- Why aren't you hitting me?

44:17.780 --> 44:18.989
Hit me!

44:19.615 --> 44:20.824
You piece of shit!

44:23.744 --> 44:25.579
You come with me. Now!

44:26.205 --> 44:27.873
Jae-in...

44:30.501 --> 44:33.420
- Please stop.
- Let go. Get out of the way!

44:33.962 --> 44:35.172
I'm going to kill him.

44:36.465 --> 44:37.716
Get back here!

44:38.133 --> 44:39.510
Let go of me!

44:40.886 --> 44:43.222
Are you kidding me right now?

44:43.597 --> 44:45.349
You acted like your life was put together,

44:46.225 --> 44:47.810
but this is how it's been?

44:48.352 --> 44:50.396
Just look at yourself!

44:51.814 --> 44:54.942
I'm sorry, Jae-in.

45:00.155 --> 45:01.782
Seo-in...

45:09.998 --> 45:12.793
I thought you were too mad to see me.

45:15.170 --> 45:16.338
Are you here to vent again?

45:19.049 --> 45:20.509
If I do, will you hear me out?

45:25.055 --> 45:27.141
Are you worried that
I'll start up music again?

45:29.560 --> 45:30.936
Forget about a music career.

45:31.520 --> 45:33.147
I'm worried
you'll do something even worse.

45:34.022 --> 45:37.484
Those few photos showed a dynamic story.

45:38.068 --> 45:39.403
It's nothing.

45:42.072 --> 45:44.491
He's an alumnus
of the college I graduated.

45:45.617 --> 45:46.952
Then you know him?

45:47.494 --> 45:48.787
He's a few years my junior.

45:49.455 --> 45:52.458
I introduced the two
and now they're friends.

45:52.541 --> 45:54.001
There's nothing more to it.

45:55.502 --> 45:58.464
You are one understanding friend.

46:01.049 --> 46:03.343
What job will you offer
Jeong-in's dad after his retirement?

46:05.929 --> 46:07.681
Get him a good one while you're at it.

46:09.391 --> 46:11.727
Why? Aren't you competent enough
to get the girl by yourself?

46:13.937 --> 46:17.816
Who cares about a shoddy deal
when it gets you what you want?

46:19.610 --> 46:20.777
It's your specialty, isn't it?

46:26.158 --> 46:27.993
You admitted it too after meeting her.

46:29.328 --> 46:30.370
Right.

46:31.246 --> 46:33.457
Well, she's not an easy fish to catch.

46:34.249 --> 46:37.544
I'm willing to go this far
because it's her.

46:37.628 --> 46:42.674
Just so you know, I don't lag behind
other men that are out there.

46:43.592 --> 46:45.052
It's why I can't let this go.

46:46.261 --> 46:48.096
I can't become a pathetic loser.

46:51.391 --> 46:54.770
Do you think that I led a dirty life?

46:58.148 --> 46:59.650
You hated that I was like Mom, right?

47:03.445 --> 47:05.405
Well, I'll live like you from now on.

47:09.660 --> 47:11.036
Give her dad a decent position,

47:12.246 --> 47:13.789
and I'll do the rest.

47:40.816 --> 47:42.568
Don't break up with Ji-ho.

47:46.029 --> 47:50.242
Enjoy a long and happy life
with the man you love.

48:13.181 --> 48:14.808
You should grab some lunch first.

48:14.891 --> 48:17.311
My classes are in the afternoon,
so I have time.

48:17.394 --> 48:19.062
I hope you pass this time.

48:19.521 --> 48:21.356
It might just encourage Ye-seul.

48:22.816 --> 48:25.068
I'm thinking about
studying for the test too.

48:25.152 --> 48:27.070
Anyway, I wish you luck.

48:27.446 --> 48:28.697
Right, we should...

48:31.575 --> 48:33.076
I'm not here for supplements.

48:33.660 --> 48:35.495
Pride isn't a luxury
you can afford right now.

48:36.371 --> 48:38.081
- We'll get going.
- Enjoy your lunch.

48:38.165 --> 48:39.207
Sure thing.

48:39.958 --> 48:43.503
Seriously. I'm just here to talk.

48:44.004 --> 48:46.590
Then talk.
What was that about telling me to run?

48:47.174 --> 48:48.258
That was just a joke.

48:49.259 --> 48:51.178
Because Jae-in is
seriously rooting for you guys.

48:52.179 --> 48:55.265
It doesn't seem like one.
Tell her I'll consider it.

48:55.349 --> 48:58.018
As if. Run away? You?

48:58.310 --> 48:59.519
You're too decent for that.

49:00.812 --> 49:02.105
I'll try the bad boy thing.

49:20.374 --> 49:24.920
SUYEONG FOUNDATION ORGANIZATION CHART

49:25.003 --> 49:26.922
CHIEF DIRECTOR KWON YEONG-GUK

50:26.982 --> 50:28.150
There. Lean back.

50:28.942 --> 50:30.485
- Is that comfortable?
- Yes.

50:31.695 --> 50:34.489
- Have fun with your dad.
- And Ms. Lee.

50:34.614 --> 50:36.992
What? Oh, yes. Of course.

50:39.202 --> 50:42.080
Don't let him eat anything too cold.

50:42.164 --> 50:43.457
I packed some barley tea.

50:43.540 --> 50:46.001
This isn't my first time,
so what's with all the fuss?

50:46.293 --> 50:47.669
She must want to come with.

50:48.920 --> 50:49.838
Eun-u, let's get going.

50:50.255 --> 50:51.173
We won't be late.

50:51.965 --> 50:54.426
If he gets fussy, head back and--

50:54.509 --> 50:57.262
He'll be heading out tomorrow
at this rate. Get yourself going.

50:57.345 --> 50:58.847
- We'll get going then.
- Bye.

51:00.348 --> 51:02.309
Eun-u, have a good time.

51:03.268 --> 51:05.145
- Eun-u!
- Have fun.

51:05.353 --> 51:06.688
- Have a safe trip.
- Sure.

51:06.772 --> 51:08.148
- Be careful out there.
- Sure.

51:12.110 --> 51:14.571
Maybe we should've
told him to leave Eun-u.

51:15.363 --> 51:17.616
She's the one who wanted Eun-u to come.

51:18.867 --> 51:20.076
She's just saying that.

51:20.786 --> 51:22.662
What if she gets annoyed that he's there?

51:23.246 --> 51:26.416
Words can become reality if you keep
saying it, so stop thinking so negatively.

51:39.930 --> 51:40.972
Hi, Eun-u!

51:43.225 --> 51:45.811
Hey, you didn't forget. Thanks.

51:55.195 --> 51:56.363
Why aren't you saying hi?

51:57.364 --> 51:58.406
Hi.

51:59.783 --> 52:00.992
Are you upset about something?

52:02.160 --> 52:04.412
Of course not.
You should put on your seat belt.

52:07.082 --> 52:10.168
Eun-u, it seems like
your dad's sulking for no reason.

52:11.586 --> 52:12.629
That's stupid.

52:19.719 --> 52:21.054
You'll burn a hole in my face.

52:22.055 --> 52:23.682
"You'll burn a hole in my face."

52:26.601 --> 52:27.936
I'm already worried about today.

52:31.773 --> 52:33.483
It's okay to be a bit late for weddings.

52:34.651 --> 52:36.069
I've left the house.

52:37.946 --> 52:39.990
All right. I'll see you soon.

53:37.088 --> 53:38.131
One, two, three!

53:39.674 --> 53:40.926
Eun-u!

53:45.764 --> 53:48.975
All right. Eun-u, wait for us.

53:50.602 --> 53:52.520
Eun-u.

53:53.104 --> 53:54.397
Okay, good.

53:57.317 --> 53:58.693
Let's go.

54:33.436 --> 54:35.313
Good job.

54:50.370 --> 54:52.622
Do you think Eun-u will remember this day?

54:56.292 --> 54:58.378
He will. I'm sure of it.

55:10.890 --> 55:11.891
Eun-u.

55:12.851 --> 55:14.060
Here you go.

55:34.456 --> 55:37.083
Change the photo you have by your bed
to this one.

55:44.299 --> 55:45.300
My first attempt failed.

56:06.029 --> 56:07.655
- Dad.
- Yes?

56:08.114 --> 56:11.576
Ms. Lee asked if I'd like her

56:11.868 --> 56:13.620
as my mom.

56:23.797 --> 56:24.798
So...

56:25.715 --> 56:27.884
- what did you say?
- "Yes."

56:35.058 --> 56:36.893
Good job. That's a good answer.

56:37.560 --> 56:38.812
Can you stay here for a while?

56:57.038 --> 56:58.915
I'm not one with high self-esteem.

57:01.918 --> 57:04.087
I'm not embarrassed about
being rejected once.

57:07.382 --> 57:08.383
Jeong-in.

57:09.342 --> 57:10.802
You know I'm quite mean,

57:13.847 --> 57:15.181
and I toss and turn in bed.

57:17.016 --> 57:18.101
What else?

57:20.186 --> 57:21.187
Are you...

57:23.648 --> 57:24.649
really...

57:26.401 --> 57:27.694
coming to us?

57:29.571 --> 57:30.572
Yes.

57:31.698 --> 57:33.700
I can't wait until I have gray hair.

57:50.216 --> 57:52.886
Just so you know,
I'm going to be a tough wife.

57:55.263 --> 57:56.306
I already know that.

59:25.853 --> 59:27.355
The door is opening.

59:53.506 --> 59:54.632
First floor.

59:58.303 --> 59:59.345
Going up.

01:00:25.246 --> 01:00:27.332
You should give him a call this time.

01:00:28.249 --> 01:00:30.293
He said he'll be heading back
after dinner.

01:00:30.376 --> 01:00:32.587
Then what's taking him so long?

01:00:33.588 --> 01:00:35.965
Eun-u's with his dad,
so why are you worried?

01:00:36.049 --> 01:00:37.717
Well, she's with them too.

01:00:38.217 --> 01:00:40.428
It's nice that
she's spending more time with Eun-u.

01:00:43.431 --> 01:00:44.682
Will she marry him?

01:00:46.225 --> 01:00:47.268
If she does,

01:00:48.102 --> 01:00:49.437
I couldn't be any happier.

01:00:49.520 --> 01:00:51.189
You don't even know what she's like.

01:00:53.524 --> 01:00:55.193
I wonder if she'll come here later.

01:00:55.610 --> 01:00:58.154
Maybe I'll ask her to come inside.

01:01:01.032 --> 01:01:02.909
Wouldn't it be too sudden?

01:01:02.992 --> 01:01:04.827
You're just as curious, aren't you?

01:01:04.911 --> 01:01:06.329
Of course, I am.

01:01:06.579 --> 01:01:08.998
He's never been this close
with anyone before.

01:01:09.582 --> 01:01:11.042
It's why I'm more worried.

01:01:13.127 --> 01:01:16.297
What if he gives her his heart
only to have it broken again?

01:01:16.381 --> 01:01:17.799
How will we stitch it back up?

01:01:18.383 --> 01:01:20.635
Eun-u will be affected this time too.

01:01:21.552 --> 01:01:23.471
Do you know why I was fussy this morning?

01:01:24.347 --> 01:01:25.723
It's because of that reason.

01:01:37.110 --> 01:01:38.695
Do you not know anything about this?

01:01:40.655 --> 01:01:42.824
Of course, I don't. How would I know?

01:01:43.449 --> 01:01:44.492
Damn it.

01:01:49.414 --> 01:01:51.290
No, let me.

01:01:53.084 --> 01:01:55.628
- Get her over here immediately.
- Sure.

01:01:56.087 --> 01:01:57.880
She had better show up!

01:02:02.218 --> 01:02:04.595
I didn't offer to drive because of Eun-u.

01:02:06.139 --> 01:02:09.016
Would I even be tired?
I doubt I'll even sleep at night.

01:02:09.809 --> 01:02:11.310
I'm the one who won't be sleeping.

01:02:11.811 --> 01:02:13.604
My first proposal was rejected, remember?

01:02:15.022 --> 01:02:17.650
I told you I got the gist of it.

01:02:18.109 --> 01:02:20.820
Whatever. I'd still be single
if it weren't for Eun-u.

01:02:23.281 --> 01:02:24.657
I'm proud of you, son.

01:02:33.499 --> 01:02:35.793
- Yes?
- Your dad found out.

01:02:36.127 --> 01:02:37.545
You should run away.

01:03:14.707 --> 01:03:17.877
If it wasn't Gi-seok,
who could've done such a thing?

01:03:17.960 --> 01:03:19.086
Gi-seok's father.

01:03:19.170 --> 01:03:22.340
I need to talk to your father. It's best
if you're there too, so be there.

01:03:22.423 --> 01:03:24.008
I took it without any meaning.

01:03:24.091 --> 01:03:26.511
- I should've returned it earlier.
- What's so great about him?

01:03:26.594 --> 01:03:28.763
I don't need anything else.
Just come back to me.

01:03:28.888 --> 01:03:30.598
- Bring him home.
- No.

01:03:30.848 --> 01:03:32.141
But you said you'll marry him.

01:03:32.225 --> 01:03:33.684
I know you're planning to

01:03:33.768 --> 01:03:35.311
humiliate him and drive him away.

01:03:35.394 --> 01:03:37.480
You don't have to date Gi-seok.

01:03:37.605 --> 01:03:39.690
I'll give up the job at the foundation
after I retire.

01:03:39.774 --> 01:03:40.817
I can't give him up.

01:03:40.900 --> 01:03:44.946
Please tell Seo-in
to persuade Jeong-in for me.

01:03:45.029 --> 01:03:48.115
I'll make it worth your while.
I sincerely mean it.

01:03:48.616 --> 01:03:50.618
I know I don't say it,
but I'm worried too.

01:03:50.701 --> 01:03:52.245
I'm even terrified at times.

01:03:52.328 --> 01:03:54.163
I'm scared she'll show up
and demand Eun-u back.

01:03:54.997 --> 01:03:56.207
Yu-mi's married.
